{"tid":2382882,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】多國議員聯署回應港共大搜捕","createTime":"2021-01-27T14:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T13:37:39.000Z","uid":234894,"like":78,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"83e7d07e812e4cfb6af495b422c9cb47711a095f","tid":2382882,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T14:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e2juUb1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe2juUb1.png&h=6ea7c8f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方上月以《國安法》中顛覆政權罪搜捕55名民主派初選協調人和參選人，觸發國際社會關注。來自美國、英國、加拿大和澳洲共17個國會議員參與聯署聲明，促中共政權和港府停止政治檢控，並支持他們所屬的政府迅速以行動回應濫捕。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>宣佈流亡海外的立法會前議員梁頌恆</strong>、<strong>現獲英國政治庇護的鄭文傑以及由支持香港民主發展的澳洲香港人「澳港聯」</strong>日前發起聯署，最新共有17人簽署，包括美國共和黨眾議員巴克（Ken Buck）和佩里（Scott Perry），以及英國「跨黨派國會香港小組」聯席主席貝內特女男爵（Baroness Bennett）和副主席Andrew Rosindell 等。<br />\n<br />\n聯署形容，上月政權大搜捕民主派是《國安法》實施以來最大型的鎮壓，批香港政府懲罰在極權下爭取自由的人（These mass arrests present the biggest crackdown on dissent in Hong Kong since the passing of the NSL last year, and shows the Hong Kong government&rsquo;s impunity for those fighting for freedom under authoritarian rule.）。他們敦促中國和香港政府停止對香港民主派人士進行政治起訴，並要求所屬政府以行動回應。<br />\n<br />\n其中兩名美國眾議員在聯署時特別關注民主動力司庫、居港美籍人權律師關尚義（John Clancey）被捕一事，至於加拿大議員則在聲明中提及律師兼民主黨九龍城區議員黃國桐被指涉嫌協助12港人而被捕。英國議員的聲明則提到，會促請政府履行其對《中英聯合聲明》中所保障的權利和自由。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210127/MS2MEEVHGRAYLPXOD2RBOETTU4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210127%2FMS2MEEVHGRAYLPXOD2RBOETTU4%2F&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=381268b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210127%2FMS2MEEVHGRAYLPXOD2RBOETTU4%2F&h=1f29c23d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210127/MS2MEEVHGRAYLPXOD2RBOETTU4/</a><br />\n<br />\nPage:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Freehongkongdemocrats\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFreehongkongdemocrats&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=0a0448f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Freehongkongdemocrats</a>"},{"pid":"8e5f5829221150b26436700e28e99c33e8c5747b","tid":2382882,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T14:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151b5848cce6942a3ba1055088e88050e5f1b649","tid":2382882,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T14:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2404178b3269a728573ef1059c40f9e48de03fa5","tid":2382882,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T14:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930d64a01692eeaaa500f131bc33cadcaa69076a","tid":2382882,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T14:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac2f5f553d2a8008ff0f09c6e581bd67d7499b9","tid":2382882,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T14:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj